snippet.title: Type to Continue - Trailer
snippet.description:
A short, binaural, typing-horror game released on Itch.io.

Available Now!
https://shakles.itch.io/type-to-continue

You're alone in a seemingly infinite hotel hallway, and you are tasked with writing down the names of the tenants, but.... something is following you.

Listen to the OST here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X0SAA0iRCaU
